definition.value: A leukotriene that is (5S,7E,9E,11Z,14Z)-5-hydroxyicosa-7,9,11,14-tetraenoic acid in which a glutathionyl group is attached at position 6 via a sulfide linkage.
A monoterpenoid that is (2E,6E)-octa-2,6-dienal substituted by methyl groups at positions 3 and 7.
A derivative of L-serine having a 3-O-D-galactosyl-N-acetyl-beta-D-galactosaminyl moiety attached to the side-chain oxygen.
